  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch34-01",
      "text": "C'est la Ligue.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a vaulted stone chamber, hooded Ligue members sit around a steampunk brass conference table facing the viewer, a large wall map marked with scientist locations behind them. A candelabra at the center of the table is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Candlelight flickers across hooded faces, secretive and conspiratorial mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "ligue_revealed",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-02",
      "text": "La Ligue a besoin des savants.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "ligue_revealed",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-03",
      "text": "La Ligue cherche les savants parce qu'elle a besoin de tout.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "ligue_revealed",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-04",
      "text": "On a besoin de tout car les savants ont disparu.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "ligue_revealed",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-05",
      "text": "Il faut agir car on ne va pas rater.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "ligue_revealed",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-06",
      "text": "Les ancêtres ont disparu.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a steampunk study, Avril stands facing the viewer before a brass display board showing the Franklin family tree, her finger tracing the portraits of her ancestors. The engraved ancestor portraits on the board are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Warm oil lamp light illuminates the faded sepia portraits, melancholy and reverent mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "ancestors",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-07",
      "text": "On a raté le travail.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "ancestors",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-08",
      "text": "C'est l'âge des ancêtres qui ont disparu.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "ancestors",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-09",
      "text": "Avril pense à ses ancêtres.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "ancestors",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-10",
      "text": "On a raté.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "ancestors",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-11",
      "text": "La Ligue a commis une chose.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a wrecked scientist's laboratory after a botched raid, Ligue agents stand amid the aftermath facing the viewer, scorched equipment and broken glass scattered around them. An open hidden passage where the scientist escaped is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Hazy daylight filters through a cracked window, frustrated and regretful mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mistakes",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-12",
      "text": "Il faut reprendre le travail.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mistakes",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-13",
      "text": "On a commis une chose.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mistakes",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-14",
      "text": "La Ligue reprend tout.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mistakes",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-15",
      "text": "L'âge ne change rien.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mistakes",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch34-16",
      "text": "On va procéder.",
      "imagePrompt": "On a steampunk city street, two Ligue agents face the viewer at a laboratory door, one holding up official documents while the other checks a clipboard. The stamped documents in the agent's hand are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Overcast daylight and gas streetlamps light the scene, methodical and relentless mood.",
